PRIVACY POLICY – Culturxp
Privacy Policy – Culturxp Studio
The applications designed & published by culturxp Studio have no means of collecting nor transmitting any sensitive user data. The data that is generated by these applications contains only user configuration information, & is only accessible by the user.
Delete My Data
As part of our commitment to data privacy and security, we are conducting a data deletion process. To ensure the accurate and thorough removal of your data from our records, please visit the following page
https://culturxp.com/data-deletion
Culturxp (“us”, “we”, or “our”) operates the Culturxp Studio (hereinafter referred to as the “Service”).
Information
Collection and Use
The applications designed & published by Culturxp Studio have no means of collecting nor transmitting any sensitive user data. The data that is generated by these applications contains only user configuration information, & is only accessible by the user.
The Watch Face itself communicates with the phone via Google Play Services.
Link to privacy policy of third party service providers used by the app:
